reviewText: movie very predictable but being a Sharon Gless fan had to see it we enjoyed it!
Arrived in a timely manner and was as described. DVD plays well. Really like the movie :)

This is a great movie full of excitement.  It is a movie that will interest both men and women.  It has many scenes with a lot of flying in it.  It stars Sharon Gless from Cagney and Lacey, so you know the acting is first rate.  if you want a good movie that will maintain your interest, this is one for you.  I highly recommend it.
Love this movie... based somewhat on Sally Ride. Saw it when it first came out & been waiting for DVD. Sharon Gless is always a winner!! Thanks!!
